{"word":"ψύχω","slug":"ψύχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ψύχω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to breathe, blow</i>, <el>ἦκα μάλα ψύξασα</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>commonly, <i>to make cold, cool, refrigerate</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to grow cold</i> or <i>cool</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to dry, make dry</i>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}